name: Crave Book!
description:
Crave is a super fun read, featuring Portland women business owners in all sorts of industries....MegExpressions is on page 115!  

The Crave book came out in 2011 (late summer) and you can purchase it from this website for only $10 with any purchase!  

(if you want the discounted price let me know so I can change the price for you).  ~ meg
